  "title": "Guide: urlSync",
  "body": "There should be a dedicated section in the guide about url sync.\r\n\r\nIt should explains:\r\n- [ ] what is the default behavior\r\n- [ ] how to only set some attributes (trackedParameters)\r\n- [ ] how to rename attributes\r\n- [ ] how to add and sync more parameters (like custom_param=avalue)\r\n- [x] what is is_v?\r\n- [ ] when do you need to use the hash method (< IE9)\r\n- [ ] Document default aliases\r\n",
